===Definitions===
{{zh-hanzi}}

# to [[be called]]
#: {{zh-x|你 叫 什么 名字？|What is your name?}}
#: {{zh-x|這 叫 什么？|How do you '''call''' this? / What '''is it called'''?}}
# to [[call]], to [[name]]
#: {{zh-x|我們 經常 叫 他 的 綽號。|We often '''call''' him by his nickname.}}
#: {{zh-x|我 可以 叫 他 ^@戴夫 嗎？|May I '''call''' him Dave?}}
# to [[call]] {{qualifier|someone}}
#: {{zh-x|叫 警察|to call the police}}
#: {{zh-x|要是 需要 什麼，我 就 叫 你。|I' ll '''call''' you if anything is needed.}}
# to [[cry]], to [[shout]]
#: {{zh-x|狗叫|bark}}
#: {{zh-x|她 高興 地 叫 起來，投入 了 她 母親 的 懷抱。|With a '''cry''' of joy, she fell into her mother's arms.}}
# to [[hail]], to [[greet]]
# to [[ask]], to [[order]]
#: {{zh-x|叫 他 待 在 家裡。|'''Ask''' her to stay home.}}
#: {{zh-x|醫生 叫 他 休息 幾 天。|The doctor '''told''' him to lay off a couple of days.}}
# to [[hire]], to [[call]] {{qualifier|a taxi}}, to [[order]] {{qualifier|in a restaurant, in a shop}}
#: {{zh-x|我 給 你 叫 什么 菜？ 肉 排 還是 魚？|What shall I '''order''' for you? Steak or fish?}}
# {{non-gloss definition|(used in a passive sentence to introduce the agent)}} [[by]]
#: {{zh-x|莊稼 叫 大水 沖 跑 了。|The crops were washed away '''by''' the flood.}}

====Usage notes====
* {{sense|to call, to be called}} when used for a person, 叫 refer to surname and / or name.

